	,SRC_fact_test.V_COLLECTED_AT_DATE AS V_COLLECTED_AT_DATE

	,SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_ID AS TEST_TYPE_ID
	,SRC_dim_test_detail.STATUS AS STATUS
	,SRC_dim_program.PROGRAM_ID AS PROGRAM_ID
	,SRC_fact_order_line.OWNER_USER_KEY AS OWNER_USER_KEY
	,SRC_fact_order_line.REORDERED_TEST_ID AS REORDERED_TEST_ID
	,SRC_dim_screening_offering.SCREENING_METHOD_KIND AS SCREENING_METHOD_KIND
  FROM 
	$TFORM_SRC_fact_test SRC_fact_test 

 INNER JOIN
 $TFORM_SRC_dim_lab SRC_dim_lab 
ON
(SRC_fact_test.LAB_KEY = SRC_dim_lab.LAB_KEY ) 

 INNER JOIN
 $TFORM_SRC_dim_test_type SRC_dim_test_type 
ON
(SRC_fact_test.TEST_TYPE_KEY = SRC_dim_test_type.TEST_TYPE_KEY ) 

 INNER JOIN
 $TFORM_SRC_dim_test_detail SRC_dim_test_detail 
ON
(SRC_fact_test.TEST_DETAIL_KEY = SRC_dim_test_detail.TEST_DETAIL_KEY ) 

 INNER JOIN
 $TFORM_SRC_dim_program SRC_dim_program 
ON
(SRC_fact_test.PROGRAM_KEY = SRC_dim_program.PROGRAM_KEY ) 

 LEFT OUTER JOIN
 $TFORM_SRC_fact_order_line SRC_fact_order_line 
ON
(SRC_fact_test.TEST_ID = SRC_fact_order_line.REORDERED_TEST_ID 
) 

 INNER JOIN
 $TFORM_SRC_dim_screening_offering SRC_dim_screening_offering 
ON
(SRC_fact_test.SCREENING_OFFERING_KEY = SRC_dim_screening_offering.SCREENING_OFFERING_KEY) 
) 
,  PIDs 
 AS 
( 
SELECT 
	JNR_SourceTables.TEST_ID AS TEST_ID
	,JNR_SourceTables.USER_KEY AS USER_KEY
	,JNR_SourceTables.IS_DELETED AS IS_DELETED

	JNR_SourceTables

,  JNR_KeyTables 
AS 
( 
SELECT 
	PIDs.TEST_ID AS TEST_ID
	,PIDs.USER_KEY AS USER_KEY
	,PIDs.IS_DELETED AS IS_DELETED
	,PIDs.V_SHIPPED_DATE AS V_SHIPPED_DATE
	,PIDs.V_CREATED_AT_DATE AS V_CREATED_AT_DATE
	,PIDs.V_COLLECTED_AT_DATE AS V_COLLECTED_AT_DATE

	,SRC_dim_intervention.INTERVENTION_KEY AS INTERVENTION_KEY

 LEFT OUTER JOIN
 SRC_dim_person

(PIDs.V_PERSON_PID = SRC_dim_person.PERSON_PID) 

 LEFT OUTER JOIN
 SRC_dim_partner 
ON
(PIDs.V_PARTNER_PID = SRC_dim_partner.PARTNER_PID ) 

 LEFT OUTER JOIN
 SRC_dim_offering 
ON
(PIDs.V_OFFERING_PID = SRC_dim_offering.OFFERING_PID AND PIDs.V_MODALITY = SRC_dim_offering.MODALITY) 

 LEFT OUTER JOIN
 SRC_dim_intervention 
ON
(PIDs.V_INTERVENTION_PID = SRC_dim_intervention.INTERVENTION_PID ) 
) 
,  GetKeys_Dates_Performance 
 AS 
( 
SELECT 
	CASE WHEN JNR_KeyTables.PERSON_KEY  IS NULL THEN -1  ELSE JNR_KeyTables.PERSON_KEY END AS V_PERSON_KEY
	,CASE WHEN JNR_KeyTables.INTERVENTION_KEY   IS NULL THEN -1    ELSE JNR_KeyTables.INTERVENTION_KEY  END AS V_INTERVENTION_KEY
	,CASE WHEN JNR_KeyTables.OFFERING_KEY  IS NULL THEN -1  ELSE JNR_KeyTables.OFFERING_KEY  END AS V_OFFERING_KEY

	,JNR_KeyTables.V_CREATED_AT_DATE AS V_ORDER_DATE
	,trim(JNR_KeyTables.status ) AS V_STATUS

	,0 AS V_LAST_ORDER_IND
	,JNR_KeyTables.is_deleted AS V_IS_DELETED
	,CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS CREATED_AT
	,CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS UPDATED_AT
	,'V3' AS SOURCE_SYSTEM
 FROM 
	JNR_KeyTables
)MERGE $DO_GHL1_MS_IDM_FACT_OFFERING_INSTANCE TGT_fact_offering_instance 
 USING GetKeys_Dates_Performance GetKeys_Dates_Performance 
  ON TGT_fact_offering_instance.person_key = GetKeys_Dates_Performance.V_PERSON_KEY AND 
TGT_fact_offering_instance.intervention_key = GetKeys_Dates_Performance.V_INTERVENTION_KEY AND 
TGT_fact_offering_instance.offering_key = GetKeys_Dates_Performance.V_OFFERING_KEY AND

 WHEN MATCHED THEN

	status = GetKeys_Dates_Performance.V_STATUS
	,order_date = GetKeys_Dates_Performance.V_ORDER_DATE
	,service_date = GetKeys_Dates_Performance.V_SERVICE_DATE
	,mailed_date = GetKeys_Dates_Performance.V_MAILED_DATE
	,reordered_ind = GetKeys_Dates_Performance.V_REORDERED_IND
	,last_order_ind = GetKeys_Dates_Performance.V_LAST_ORDER_IND
	,updated_at = GetKeys_Dates_Performance.UPDATED_AT
	,is_deleted = GetKeys_Dates_Performance.V_IS_DELETED
	,source_system = GetKeys_Dates_Performance.SOURCE_SYSTEM
 WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN 
INSERT
(partner_key,intervention_key,person_key,offering_key,status,order_date,service_date,mailed_date,reordered_ind,last_order_ind,created_at,updated_at,is_deleted,source_system)
VALUES (
GetKeys_Dates_Performance.V_PARTNER_KEY,
GetKeys_Dates_Performance.V_INTERVENTION_KEY,
GetKeys_Dates_Performance.V_PERSON_KEY,
GetKeys_Dates_Performance.V_OFFERING_KEY,
GetKeys_Dates_Performance.V_STATUS,
GetKeys_Dates_Performance.V_ORDER_DATE,
GetKeys_Dates_Performance.V_SERVICE_DATE,
GetKeys_Dates_Performance.V_MAILED_DATE,
GetKeys_Dates_Performance.V_REORDERED_IND,
GetKeys_Dates_Performance.V_LAST_ORDER_IND,
GetKeys_Dates_Performance.CREATED_AT,
GetKeys_Dates_Performance.UPDATED_AT,
GetKeys_Dates_Performance.V_IS_DELETED,
GetKeys_Dates_Performance.SOURCE_SYSTEM)#SEMICOLON_DELIM#

WITH SRC_fact_offering_instance  AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_fact_offering_instance.partner_key AS PARTNER_KEY
	,SRC_fact_offering_instance.person_key AS PERSON_KEY
	,SRC_fact_offering_instance.offering_key AS OFFERING_KEY

	,SRC_fact_offering_instance.order_date AS ORDER_DATE
	,SRC_fact_offering_instance.person_key  AS V_PERSON_KEY
	,SRC_fact_offering_instance.intervention_key  AS V_INTERVENTION_KEY
	,SRC_fact_offering_instance.offering_key  AS V_OFFERING_KEY
	,SRC_fact_offering_instance.partner_key  AS V_PARTNER_KEY
 FROM 
	$DO_GHL1_MS_IDM_FACT_OFFERING_INSTANCE SRC_fact_offering_instance  
 WHERE 
	SRC_fact_offering_instance.is_deleted = 0 
) 
,  Generate_Row_Num 
 AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_fact_offering_instance.V_PERSON_KEY AS V_PERSON_KEY
	,SRC_fact_offering_instance.V_INTERVENTION_KEY AS V_INTERVENTION_KEY
	,SRC_fact_offering_instance.V_OFFERING_KEY AS V_OFFERING_KEY
	,SRC_fact_offering_instance.V_PARTNER_KEY AS V_PARTNER_KEY
	,ROW_NUMBER() OVER
(
PARTITION BY
	SRC_fact_offering_instance.PERSON_KEY , SRC_fact_offering_instance.OFFERING_KEY,SRC_fact_offering_instance.PARTNER_KEY
ORDER BY
       SRC_fact_offering_instance.PERSON_KEY , SRC_fact_offering_instance.OFFERING_KEY,SRC_fact_offering_instance.PARTNER_KEY, SRC_fact_offering_instance.ORDER_DATE  desc, SRC_fact_offering_instance.MAILED_DATE  desc
) AS ROW_NUM
	,CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS UPDATED_AT
 FROM 
	SRC_fact_offering_instance
)

 SET
	TGT_fact_offering_instance_UPD_$$RUNID.last_order_ind = Generate_Row_Num.ROW_NUM
	,TGT_fact_offering_instance_UPD_$$RUNID.updated_at = Generate_Row_Num.UPDATED_AT
FROM
	$DO_GHL1_MS_IDM_FACT_OFFERING_INSTANCE TGT_fact_offering_instance_UPD_$$RUNID
JOIN
Generate_Row_Num Generate_Row_Num
ON
TGT_fact_offering_instance_UPD_$$RUNID.partner_key = Generate_Row_Num.V_PARTNER_KEY AND TGT_fact_offering_instance_UPD_$$RUNID.intervention_key = Generate_Row_Num.V_INTERVENTION_KEY AND TGT_fact_offering_instance_UPD_$$RUNID.person_key = Generate_Row_Num.V_PERSON_KEY AND TGT_fact_offering_instance_UPD_$$RUNID.offering_key = Generate_Row_Num.V_OFFERING_KEY
 AND 
Generate_Row_Num.ROW_NUM =1
